title: 4 bedroom home for rent in Hinckley MN
posting_body: ['Incredible hard to find 4 bedroom home for rent in Hinckley MN.', 'This house is located on a beautiful tree covered corner lot.', 'Plenty of off street parking, a 2 car garage and an outbuilding.', 'The house is newly painted and move in ready.', 'Spacious eat in kitchen.', 'Washer and Dryer hookups in the basement.', 'The hidden gem of this property is the stand alone 3rd building.', 'It is a man cave / she shed located on the back of the property.', 'It features an extra garage space below and a room to relax or entertain above the garage.', 'We check income, credit, criminal and rental history and references.', 'Renter pays all utilities and renters insurance, plus responsible for snow removal and yard maintenance.', '$1800 deposit plus 1st month rent on 1 year lease agreement.', 'Only 75 minutes South of Duluth.', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'for appointment.', 'Only minutes from the Hinckley Casino.', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'for appointment.', '17 Minutes to Pine City', '18 Minutes to Sandstone', '24 Minutes to Mora', '25 Minutes to Rush City', '36 Minutes to Ogilvie', '48 Minutes to Forrest Lake', '49 Minutes to Cambridge', '1 Hour 9 Minutes to Duluth']
